cs.DC, cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.CY, cs.CR

This paper discusses the development of a data ecosystem for democratizing data science and artificial intelligence. It involves the exchange of diverse data-related assets, algorithms, processing software, compute resources, and domain knowledge. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Databases (cs.DB), Cybersecurity (cs.CY), and Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) sub-categories.
